"Text",ExpressionUUID->"19368402-193a-4457-ba4c-3e8322c7783c"],

Cell["Safe Algebraic Cessation Lemma", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"4d1fe830-2dce-4919-9636-23f5a1711292"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Write the inherited ledger projectors as ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["P_i = Pi_i^(A) \\otimes 1_B",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"b3485573-9b34-4027-8ce0-2db95aa349fb"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"2dfffd24-bdf6-4263-8d94-648bb1cfafec"],
 "and let the post-split channel be ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["E(X) = Sum_alpha K_alpha X K_alpha^\\dagger",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"66617bdc-97c4-4717-958c-c3a73e3e8e96"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"e0dc5783-a82a-47f4-9520-00f93e62e492"],
 "."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"536e6850-ce75-432e-b64d-c93ba4fcec6c"],

Cell["The safe algebraic statement is:", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"fedec53b-52ba-4aa5-a326-e91eb8e28c66"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "1. If ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["E^*(P_i) = P_i",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"d2cd924a-b1c3-46cb-ae97-d300eda8084a"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"b12d30ea-59df-458c-85ce-6b8f53f33e5f"],
 " for every inherited ledger projector, then sector transfer vanishes:"
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"0ceb46a3-c92c-4fe0-99fa-d8b7a4345901"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "   ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["(1 - P_i) K_alpha P_i = 0",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"ffe514b1-988e-4846-b4af-0f654c1212ad"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"c025c3ca-e79b-4b11-bf70-6cdb1956e035"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["P_i K_alpha (1 - P_i) = 0",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"d34f9c64-b69d-484d-8c5c-488ec58adc6f"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"c0a4179d-3722-4128-9444-ef6fca534ff9"],
 "."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"19855b25-bc73-4e29-a232-578d915626cb"],

Cell["\<\
2. Hence one may choose Kraus operators block-diagonal on inherited ledger \
sectors:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"1034b678-09f6-4a1b-84e6-783a57590487"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "   ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["K_alpha = Sum_i P_i K_alpha P_i",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"ae4bbfbc-2dc1-41b8-a4aa-e40d167b402a"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"db01b9a5-f05c-4603-b6cd-ceb0d08cfe8d"],
 "."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"26235d4d-f9de-4c28-ae53-21a908ceec3c"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "3. Therefore the accepted-record algebra is frozen on ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["A",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"60890082-78dd-43ee-9979-6405dfb3b2b7"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"416a9ebd-b955-4f4e-95a2-00c84e4e49db"],
 "."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"5f672ae1-ae31-4e53-a2b7-82fb61776096"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "4. For ledger-classical inputs, the ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["A",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"82231458-6a89-4975-9e46-4d399d90b73f"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"50a66906-8640-4dc5-9070-ad8591bd1c7b"],
 "-marginal is preserved exactly."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"b710f491-6448-4d86-8a81-143ff14ff131"],

Cell["\<\
This remains the safe exact algebraic cessation layer. It is enough for \
accepted-record freezing and\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"c49fc529-c44f-4b06-a1d7-b00d30bedcab"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "ledger-classical ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["A",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"89b05be7-218e-45dc-be11-232bcf2d37e9"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"cb1578aa-1e8c-49b6-ba8d-16b9e0e61e3f"],
 "-marginal preservation. By itself it does not imply the sharper unreduced \
tensor"
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"090e7d4a-106f-4491-a150-a32c7ee3863c"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "form ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["K_alpha = Sum_i Pi_i^(A) \\otimes M_{alpha i}",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"2ac8cdd5-9ec1-4abf-ab4d-9912616ae680"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"c4ff2846-1d7b-457d-adfb-dc7e70386abb"],
 "."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"f2b53af4-024e-4d83-a592-3ebeb2934f73"],

Cell["\<\
That stronger tensor statement still needs the same minimal extra hypothesis \
as before: \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"59c89cf0-64ff-49ae-b1d5-7519eb1c05de"],

Cell["\<\
either the inherited ledger sectors are already minimal classical pointer \
sectors,\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"07ecd4cf-8009-4ecc-a204-2f99f714ffc3"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "or the action inside each ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["A",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"80accd5b-e060-4d74-b49c-eb23b4f71075"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"8a597cb7-f9fe-49ff-ae43-aad339703acf"],
 "-block is trivial on the theorem-facing ledger algebra."
}], "Item",ExpressionUUID->"ab1b4a6b-7212-471e-831e-3dc89104553e"],

Cell["\<\
For the reduced receiver verdict below, no additional within-block \
classical-pointer premise was\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"fbdc0561-7cb4-43a9-9fed-4c71af21e6a7"],

Cell["needed in the current audited family. ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"8d129e40-4f78-494d-b69a-f436d4695a65"],

Cell["Reduced-Receiver Strengthening", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"1f35aeab-a059-470a-b213-29e2b03a9f47"],

Cell["The strengthened exact target is:", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"99e37293-0152-47ee-9819-0a174faa3ded"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "1. ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["P2",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"432fbec6-6d9a-480c-96c4-ba34c65b37a1"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"94bcddd1-b5bd-4283-afec-c08d8c1444aa"],
 " algebraic cessation holds on inherited ledger sectors."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"547b1e5f-5c59-46c5-905c-599d4920a44f"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "2. ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["P3",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"ee1cb5e2-5e1e-4bbd-878c-469b1152ad95"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"e93f22f1-846c-4df1-835b-b1b965e380af"],
 " source-internal factorization holds through accepted-record history."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"02ff1acc-bd53-4afd-a466-8a733a17cdf7"],

Cell["\<\
3. Theorem-facing receiver semantics are evaluated only after a common \
reduction/projection to the\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"a5752abf-99d5-4e18-905b-e6c6f44f6f24"],

Cell["   single reduced welded boundary factor.", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"66fddaa3-8acb-4d3b-b508-d07951683392"],

Cell["\<\
The current audited family already supplies the exact reduction data: \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"94d947ba-9b7e-4a93-9984-e550d63d9b4c"],

Cell["\<\
the common reduced receiver projector is the certified welded projector\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"f0cc1685-62f7-41cb-9338-62348950b92c"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "  ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["ProfileProjectorB = {{1,0},{0,0}}",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"55c4b3c9-b050-4922-b93f-8dd82a2d3a23"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"bd16fc3a-f2da-453e-a7a9-b88f77ae9f92"],
 ", "
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"b146dff1-9cd7-4944-a57e-bd7b1d1ca876"],

Cell["that projector has exact rank one,", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"577cb985-6979-4d06-9429-3c0771e7a945"],

Cell["\<\
the representative reduced boundary image is exactly compatible with that \
line,\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"e9bb00f8-75a8-4864-9478-5813ae65afd3"],

Cell["\<\
and all ambiguity images vanish on that reduced boundary image.\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"d26e2100-df39-4d0e-a0bb-d3dfc3882966"],

Cell["\<\
So the strengthened target is not an ad hoc quotient. It is the same reduced \
welded boundary factor\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"d9b5242f-f235-4dba-80c4-3ab2d233674a"],

Cell["already used in the exact UOM boundary lane. ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"fe737fc2-7a46-4cf4-88d8-46f25cf6e5a3"],

Cell["Exact Reduced Audit", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"fde60743-7501-4d2c-a24d-b93efd5f4e3d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The exact reduced audit used the common reduced readout ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["\<\
R(block) = (Tr[block . ProfileProjectorB] / Tr[ProfileProjectorB]) \
ProfileProjectorB\
\>",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"71315c85-2f8e-481f-8cd7-a97b42d2a5a4"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"3fc6bc16-4449-44b6-81b8-89d540bc6513"],
 "with the same certified ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["ProfileProjectorB",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"0e75e80d-71c2-4775-b70b-b9493390212b"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"d72f4104-e7e7-4b7b-b148-2af7940df54e"],
 " across ledger sectors."
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"47d9ec85-cde0-46e4-b4e7-17a34983e2f6"],

Cell["The exact certificate obtained: ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"f05b60e7-ac2c-4be0-8784-918e46ac16fd"],

Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[Cell["ProfileProjectorRank = 1",
  Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
  "0c1ee5a0-8da5-4a4c-a6f7-8032cd86be70"]], \
"InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"d9701860-7ae7-43b4-b6f5-68a9358d2ada"]], "Item",\
ExpressionUUID->"364c806e-73f5-4756-9a84-0b7248c6926a"],

Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[Cell["RepresentativeBoundaryImageCompatibleQ = \
True",
  Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
  "30efa147-7b93-4293-9020-0d1a3f587a84"]], \
"InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"6203fecb-b787-48b6-9ba7-9954a62af598"]], "Item",\
ExpressionUUID->"eb63fe59-b5cb-45db-aab4-5fd121e822ba"],

Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[Cell["AmbiguityImagesAllZeroQ = True",
  Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
  "b9e28861-3e01-453d-a6b3-afc55de15879"]], \
"InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"46bdc91c-6a58-4946-be4e-752b2314cb0e"]], "Item",\
ExpressionUUID->"e1c574ba-3cf1-4681-a2e3-d079fb3e88e7"],

Cell[TextData[Cell[BoxData[Cell["ReducedResponseScalarRepresentative = 1",
  Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
  "6e1dea0f-fb47-423f-bcbd-6dad6bace167"]], \
"InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"6a8ffbfd-78c6-4d4a-9ef4-285fdf71201d"]], "Item",\
ExpressionUUID->"342e0a3e-fdee-4f54-afd3-4c07d5ca11e7"],

Cell["\<\
So the theorem-facing reduced receiver is exactly the one-dimensional welded \
line already certified\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"3126acc0-d5a2-4553-92fb-7a4b35703e4f"],

Cell["elsewhere in the current audited family. ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"c9166e3d-23cb-492d-847d-952cc0abbd87"],

Cell["Old Falsifiers After Reduction", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"94cec6b1-0d58-429f-b238-8ad28184d167"],

Cell[BoxData[
 PaneBox[
  PaneBox[
   StyleBox[
    TagBox[
     TagBox[GridBox[{
        {
         TagBox["\<\"old falsifier\"\>",
          HoldForm], 
         TagBox["\<\"status after common reduced readout\"\>",
          HoldForm], 
         TagBox["\<\"exact certificate\"\>",
          HoldForm]},
        {Cell[TextData[{
          Cell[BoxData[Cell["F2",
            Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
            "4a04dad4-13bd-4723-b6c2-3281dda28bc8"]], "InlineCode",
           ExpressionUUID->"1479cc08-346c-4e82-87c1-83baaac170eb"],
          " bridge leak"
         }],ExpressionUUID->"655ccece-1607-4897-9a6f-365a425234fb"], Cell[
         BoxData[Cell["killed by reduction",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "81bc1eaf-4ba9-4236-94fc-b9fc25ccee15"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "b1642ff0-2742-4db8-88e9-05f950c2fee0"], "\<\"the old outside-code \
witness reduces exactly to zero\"\>"},
        {Cell[TextData[{
          Cell[BoxData[Cell["F3",
            Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
            "31c1d944-6191-403a-806f-b6c55b94b8ac"]], "InlineCode",
           ExpressionUUID->"ca45f136-ed5c-4f4f-9152-69ce534c513e"],
          " covariance mismatch"
         }],ExpressionUUID->"c33517ce-a33f-493c-a951-9fb14cf2099a"], Cell[
         BoxData[Cell["killed by reduction",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "a20a2062-ed78-44b7-9446-99601a604d52"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "21fe60e1-baa7-47d6-9bf5-a168a85d41f5"], "\<\"the mismatched sector \
blocks reduce to the same welded line and, in the tested witness, to the same \
reduced scalar\"\>"},
        {Cell[TextData[{
          Cell[BoxData[Cell["F4",
            Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
            "0f8d8ef7-9547-4cca-ab96-bdf5529d76bd"]], "InlineCode",
           ExpressionUUID->"e2e32ccc-38eb-4007-bb14-c8e695a2dad2"],
          " RP/OS failure"
         }],ExpressionUUID->"4276aa2c-b82b-4b6a-ab8f-6952e4ac2b7c"], Cell[
         BoxData[Cell["killed by reduction",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "37a21959-77b6-4cef-a9be-f6e5b77bd7d1"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->"b08c5720-c2ca-425b-af2d-b4e60ec73953"], Cell[
         TextData[{
          "the unreduced reflection spectrum ",
          Cell[BoxData[Cell["{-1,1,1,1}",
            Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
            "8cf29e08-7ec0-4489-aee4-58930dc1c5be"]], "InlineCode",
           ExpressionUUID->"1686325b-4d4d-4214-86e6-b7ebcb413c22"],
          
          " becomes a positive-semidefinite reduced operator with eigenvalues \
",
          Cell[BoxData[Cell["{1,1,0,0}",
            Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
            "84691c62-7d67-4826-9bee-c246a547947c"]], "InlineCode",
           ExpressionUUID->"fd3b335a-83de-41ff-a958-fc2c89850c15"]
         }],ExpressionUUID->"b1d4acd3-e5f5-4514-9509-46b4ecfd859a"]},
        {Cell[TextData[{
          Cell[BoxData[Cell["F5",
            Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
            "d0459876-97cf-4186-84ec-757f9d4bcc40"]], "InlineCode",
           ExpressionUUID->"6ef862bc-820e-4516-8ce7-c09b871c6eb7"],
          " geometry/bookkeeping mismatch"
         }],ExpressionUUID->"d8b7c61e-d70e-4ac8-a15a-5a063ded64eb"], Cell[
         BoxData[Cell["replaced by narrower condition",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "93a83ac9-21ac-4a17-b3ab-44e61a1c907c"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "71415a47-88ba-4e44-8fd4-b238a661af25"], "\<\"hidden unreduced \
cutoffs/bookkeeping may remain, but they are not a falsifier of the reduced \
receiver target once all theorem-facing semantics pass through the same \
reduced boundary factor\"\>"}
       },
       GridBoxAlignment->{
        "Columns" -> {Center, Center, {Center}}, "Rows" -> {{Baseline}}},
       GridBoxDividers->{
        "Columns" -> {{False}}, "Rows" -> {False, True, {False}, False}},
       GridBoxSpacings->{"Columns" -> {
           Offset[0.27999999999999997`], {
            Offset[2.0999999999999996`]}, 
           Offset[0.27999999999999997`]}, "Rows" -> {
           Offset[0.2], {
            Offset[0.4]}, 
           Offset[0.2]}}],
      {None, OutputFormsDump`HeadedColumns}],
     Function[BoxForm`e$, 
      TableForm[
      BoxForm`e$, 
       TableHeadings -> {
        None, {"old falsifier", "status after common reduced readout", 
          "exact certificate"}}]]], "Text",
    StripOnInput->False,
    ShowStringCharacters->False],
   ImageMargins->{{0, 0}, {5, 5}}],
  ImageMargins->{{0, 0}, {5, 5}}]], "TextTableForm", \
"Text",ExpressionUUID->"60606341-95f1-42e9-98b7-494ba5d80a33"],

Cell["\<\
This is the key narrowing. The exact lane no longer says the unreduced \
source/tangent data must\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e257aab6-8dfd-44f4-90c3-132a1970fc9c"],

Cell["\<\
already factorize completely. It says that in the present audited family \
those unreduced differences\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"d9ccd7aa-1e70-44a3-a7cd-d00c0be0f650"],

Cell["\<\
do not generate an exact falsifier for the reduced receiver target. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"173ba33d-edfe-4873-a1fa-bfcb407141ad"],

Cell["Reduced Closure Versus Stronger Unreduced Factorization", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"e2f8acdf-5e7d-4415-a2fc-83f631c412d2"],

Cell["\<\
The audit language must now stay explicit about this distinction: \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"35873f15-eb8d-49fe-8f5c-dd81f07e6d27"],

Cell["\<\
exact reduced receiver closure may survive in the current audited family,\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"9aa4b91d-6543-4e9e-81d1-a52d8d47ef37"],

Cell["\<\
even if a stronger unreduced source/tangent factorization theorem is false,\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"f536c181-0f37-4bc1-90f0-4de3fa154b69"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "or even if that stronger theorem is simply too strong for what ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["main.tex",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"3235d53c-cb50-4a11-8bc7-23966a9c2ddd"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"30a060ed-180e-49b0-9394-faa74885fe12"],
 " actually uses on the"
}], "Item",ExpressionUUID->"26c925fe-2bf1-4353-9657-0d3e29da6d2e"],

Cell["  theorem-facing receiver side.", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e0bfd74e-911c-44fd-ade5-8f81717f0a47"],

Cell["\<\
So if source lanes later confirm seam realizations with the same \
accepted-record payload but opposite\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"95b2a059-60f9-4135-bde7-1d951635f80c"],

Cell["\<\
welded source/tangent response, that would not by itself refute this reduced \
exact packet. It would\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"ee3df80b-b310-4fab-9e1e-b2868c1b96cc"],

Cell["\<\
instead reinforce that the exact theorem-facing target must be stated as a \
reduced receiver target,\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"54b73e73-5b54-46df-bc3a-d67285b47094"],

Cell["not as full unreduced source/tangent agreement. ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"0d778b6a-1611-4a5e-b2ab-d08f1082c93c"],

Cell["Five Closure Requirements Under The Reduced Target", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"2c71d287-3c3f-4ed1-893a-c4851adae1ae"],

Cell["\<\
With the common reduced receiver clause imposed, the five first-sprint \
closure failures no longer\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"81fd2d1c-29af-43b9-996b-caba9826b3f2"],

Cell["\<\
produce an exact reduced falsifier in the current audited family: \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"6309367a-c40b-4907-8226-d1f98651c119"],

Cell[BoxData[
 PaneBox[
  PaneBox[
   StyleBox[
    TagBox[
     TagBox[GridBox[{
        {
         TagBox["\<\"requirement\"\>",
          HoldForm], 
         TagBox["\<\"reduced-target outcome\"\>",
          HoldForm], 
         TagBox["\<\"exact support\"\>",
          HoldForm]},
        {"\<\"bookkeeping closure\"\>", Cell[BoxData[
         Cell["Yes, at the theorem-facing reduced receiver level",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "746ea273-5b01-4922-b2bf-5c14b0b63394"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "72a1aaff-b5b1-4113-ad33-c28cbda73afc"], "\<\"hidden completion \
bookkeeping is no longer a reduced receiver falsifier once theorem-facing \
semantics are reduced before evaluation\"\>"},
        {"\<\"bridge-target closure\"\>", Cell[BoxData[Cell["Yes",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "751cd6e2-63bc-4767-b4db-f45f3fb469d6"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "bbdfea5e-8e42-4ca3-9a03-9792fe87bc8b"], "\<\"the old outside-code \
witness reduces exactly to zero\"\>"},
        {"\<\"one-boundary covariance closure\"\>", Cell[BoxData[
         Cell["Yes in the current family",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "aad02782-21fa-4b8b-ad7a-cb492fd7175d"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "77d82b04-39cd-4669-bdc6-d6a64301b707"], "\<\"the reduced image \
lives on one common rank-one welded line\"\>"},
        {"\<\"RP/OS closure\"\>", Cell[BoxData[
         Cell["Yes in the current family",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "490ba3d1-f2b6-46f7-aa0f-7530922212a3"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "00e4d15c-bed0-4fd7-a8b5-50d365914e76"], "\<\"the reduced \
reflection witness is positive semidefinite\"\>"},
        {"\<\"single-cutoff geometry closure\"\>", Cell[BoxData[
         Cell["Yes, as a reduced receiver statement",
           Background->None,ExpressionUUID->
           "2fe196da-2f27-4b4f-ae95-476e74528eed"]], "InlineCode",
          ExpressionUUID->
          "35c662ad-e08e-45ec-9a4f-b4e5e71000de"], "\<\"sector-dependent \
unreduced data become theorem-invisible after the common reduced boundary \
projection\"\>"}
       },
       GridBoxAlignment->{
        "Columns" -> {Center, Center, {Center}}, "Rows" -> {{Baseline}}},
       GridBoxDividers->{
        "Columns" -> {{False}}, "Rows" -> {False, True, {False}, False}},
       GridBoxSpacings->{"Columns" -> {
           Offset[0.27999999999999997`], {
            Offset[2.0999999999999996`]}, 
           Offset[0.27999999999999997`]}, "Rows" -> {
           Offset[0.2], {
            Offset[0.4]}, 
           Offset[0.2]}}],
      {None, OutputFormsDump`HeadedColumns}],
     Function[BoxForm`e$, 
      TableForm[
      BoxForm`e$, 
       TableHeadings -> {
        None, {"requirement", "reduced-target outcome", "exact support"}}]]], 
    "Text",
    StripOnInput->False,
    ShowStringCharacters->False],
   ImageMargins->{{0, 0}, {5, 5}}],
  ImageMargins->{{0, 0}, {5, 5}}]], "TextTableForm", \
"Text",ExpressionUUID->"233ef71f-2657-43ae-b3ea-fc5577956178"],

Cell["These are exact family-relative conclusions only. ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"0daf407e-b783-47d2-9237-2e5b95cfd778"],

Cell["Minimal Sufficient Package", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"2014243c-8821-402a-bdf6-63845b670683"],

Cell["\<\
In the strengthened reduced form, the exact minimal package is now:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e07394c5-26cf-4e08-9e6d-1cc906787c6f"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "1. ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["P2 algebraic cessation",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"0223206f-b366-4051-9bc8-e1e7f2bcc6df"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"fe299d8f-dc91-44f6-8685-4561928ce1dc"],
 "2. ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["\<\
P3 source-internal factorization through accepted-record history\
\>",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"ffaeeacd-322e-4ef8-ae16-073d7f937a34"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"a458db0a-ff66-4c5c-b485-586a2e2974db"],
 "3. ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["common reduced receiver clause",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"664dba3d-f11c-4720-be46-8d2de147e75a"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"55d52913-044d-4939-b6d3-aa8df0eacc1f"],
 "   all theorem-facing receiver semantics are evaluated only after the same \
reduction/projection to"
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"cf6eab8d-1157-4f9f-ac65-004846fb9321"],

Cell["   the certified one-dimensional welded boundary factor.", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e7e267fe-dae1-48fc-a894-82b1c72fc590"],

Cell["\<\
No additional within-block classical-pointer premise was needed for this \
reduced verdict in the\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"20656374-d2a0-4fc5-9603-a6874472b7b2"],

Cell["\<\
current audited family. That extra premise is still needed only if one wants \
the sharper unreduced\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"4829d123-6c49-4317-b88f-d15e3bb2fd52"],

Cell["tensor splitting statement. ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"cba4ee9c-ac50-4484-9a17-9aedcdd6a711"],

Cell["Completion Decomposition Reassessment", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"7cf611a5-cb57-45f5-b0af-82a531cb74ad"],

Cell["\<\
From the stronger reduced theorem perspective, the current exact family still \
points to the same\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"4429c470-dc8a-4dd8-9279-60f67bd965c8"],

Cell["completion conclusion: ", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"ef87618a-2b0b-49ac-b7fd-932dae09af8d"],

Cell["\<\
split core remains the meaningful strong-safe completion candidate,\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"04d2df6d-4454-4ff1-b5d2-b2bc99ecfb53"],

Cell["\<\
Gaussian augmentation still does not perform the class change,\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"f8359a87-d15e-494c-ad98-3787f500eae9"],

Cell["\<\
so split core plus the right receiver-level factorization target remains the \
natural exact\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"f297fae2-006c-4893-b7b1-d323669fb1eb"],

Cell["  class-changing package in the current audited family.", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"50ca1f65-5f2b-42d4-9434-6c71f0568490"],

Cell["\<\
This remains an exact finite-dimensional conclusion only. It is not theorem \
promotion. \
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"0832d200-0b1e-45b6-849a-3d3900faa35a"],

Cell["Acceptance State", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"e4ba261c-bf0d-47b4-8fdf-3c457008cdda"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "This lane now returns: ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["reduced target survives exact audit in current family",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"65c95305-dd90-439c-bfb3-38b208803999"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"f1a8183d-9161-4bbd-bd1d-9780ed5c8398"],
 "with the explicit scope qualifier: ",
 Cell[BoxData[Cell["\<\
No exact reduced falsifier found in the current audited family once \
theorem-facing receiver reduction is imposed.\
\>",
   Background->None,ExpressionUUID->"2d8a9832-badf-4ae2-b3e8-0ca59ff1e99c"]], 
  "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->"835d9c5c-6ffc-46ff-a128-901ab558d6be"]
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"65713960-7def-4709-9027-33f5ed07dd1b"]
},
FrontEndVersion->"14.3 for Linux x86 (64-bit) (July 8, 2025)",
